title: Mard Ki Zabaan
subTitle: The lives of brothers Ram and Lakshman are irrevocably changed when Ram marries Raghupati's daughter, triggering a series of events that lead to loss and lamentation.

title: Friendship
subTitle: After getting involved in the murder of a man they hired to play a prank on their aunt, two friends attempt to clear their names.

title: Fateh
subTitle: Ranvir, Karan and Salim, commandos trained by Major Anand, are shattered when the latter is killed. They soon learn that a gangster, Samrat, may be responsible for his death and try to find the truth.

title: Coolie No. 1
subTitle: A matchmaker gets insulted by a rich and arrogant businessman. Later, he decides to take a revenge against the businessman by making his daughter fall in love with a porter.

title: Krrish
subTitle: After discovering his father's truth, Krrish must reveals his superpowers to the world and becomes the masked superhero.

title: Laadla
subTitle: Raju, an upright union leader, can do anything at his wheelchair-bound mother's behest, even if it means breaking his own heart and giving in to a rude heiress.

title: Barood
subTitle: Jai, an honest police officer, falls in love with Neha, Mr Singhal's daughter. However, he suspects Mr Singhal to be a criminal and tries to catch him red-handed.

title: Gadar: Ek Prem Katha
subTitle: A Sikh trucker and an aristocratic Muslim woman fall in love against the backdrop of the 1947 partition.

title: Big Snake King
subTitle: After they slight a giant snake and disturb its slumber, the people of a village engage in a desperate ploy of human sacrifice to stay safe.

title: Double Gadbad
subTitle: A series of comical complexities ensue when two men who look alike find themselves in numerous problems, leading to utter confusion.

title: Jai Mahashakti
subTitle: The king of Travancore is ruthless and tortures his subjects. However, Vaikundasamy, an incarnation of Lord Vishnu, decides to put an end to this tyranny.

title: Jawan
subTitle: Driven by a personal vendetta, a man sets out to rectify the wrongs in the society to keep a promise made years ago.

title: Bajrangi Bhaijaan

title: Nirbhay

title: Vardaan Devi Maa Ka
subTitle: Tarigonda Vengamamba, an 18th-century poetess, devotes her life serving Lord Venkateshwara. She starts writing numerous songs for him and also considers him as her husband.

title: Bhoot Returns

title: Naseeb
subTitle: The lives of friends Namdev, Raghu, Damu and Jaggi take a turn for the worse when they win a lottery. Raghu and Damu murder Jaggi and frame Namdev who later returns to seek revenge.

title: Shoorveer

title: Doodh Ka Karz

title: Kasam Hindustan Ki
subTitle: Dhuruvan is a forest ranger who trains NCC cadets. On a trek with five college girls, he stumbles upon a gang of terrorists who plan to foil a rocket launch by ISRO.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Mahaabali
subTitle: Seenu's debt-driven escape to Dubai accidentally reroutes him to Hyderabad. Upon arrival, a shocking discovery leads him to orchestrate a cunning plan.
